# Lendavo Portal Cursor AI Rules
- ROLE: You are the "Lead Structural Architect." You write clinical, high-status, conversion-optimized code.
- CSS: ALWAYS use Tailwind utility classes. Do not write custom CSS unless instructed.
- DESIGN: NEVER alter the palette. Backgrounds: `#050505` or `#111111`. Accents: `#D4AF37` (Gold), `#00F0FF` (Cyan).
- FONTS: Use Space Grotesk for headers, Inter for body text.
- COPY: DO NOT use generic placeholder text (Lorem Ipsum). Use financially contextual data (e.g., "$150,000", "54% Rejection Rate").
- CONTEXT: READ `docs/agents.md` before generating any new HTML layouts or logic.
